    <briefdescription>
<para>Base implementation class for traits that need lifecycle callbacks. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Inherits from BaseObject (for reference counting / BaseHandle storage) and <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1Integration_1_1TraitInterface" kindref="compound">TraitInterface</ref> (for lifecycle callbacks). All lifecycle methods have default empty implementations; subclasses override only what they need. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
